Backend for the gtEvents mobile web application.
Language: node.js
Database: redis.io

For Facebook testing:
1.npm install facebook-js
2.npm install connect
3. edit file /etc/hosts
add one line:
127.0.0.1 kissmood.com

Test Facebook connection:
1. unauthorize gtEvents application on facebook
2. open browser, enter kissmood.com:3000/login
3. the app will ask for permission and redirect to a page showing your name
